document_data.Description:
{{Quote
|All you can think about is a [[human]] minx with wild eyes and milkbags the size of a thkaerth's!
|[[Takari Moonsnow]] refers to [[Vala Thorsdotter]] in an argument with [[Galaeron Nihmedu]]<ref name=TSumm-ch16-p234"/>
}}
These animals were known for their woolly coats and faces. Female thkaerths produced [[milk]], and their mammary glands were sometimes referred to as "milkbags".<ref name=TSumm-ch16-p234"/>

