document_data.History:
{{Quote
|I'm sure Lord Nihmedu would take a dim view of you kissing something with more wool on his face than a thkaerth.
|[[Khelben Arunsun]] to Keya Nihmedu in regards to her relationship with [[Dexon]]
}}
In the 14{{th}} century [[DR]], thkaerths were known to the [[elves]] of [[Evereska]].<ref name=TSumm-ch16-p234"/> These elves were known to compare [[Vaasan]]s to thkaerths due to their large amounts of hair. In [[1371 DR]], Galaeron Nihmedu owned a [[cloak]] made of thkaerth wool.
